query:
UPDATE prices 
SET 
  smshubPrice = ROUND(smshubPrice * 6.0),
  ourPrice = GREATEST(
    ROUND(ROUND(smshubPrice * 6.0) * (1 + 150/100)),
    100
  )
WHERE apiId = 3
